Package com.intellij.openapi.externalSystem.model.execution

Class ExternalSystemTaskExecutionSettings

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.intellij.openapi.externalSystem.model.execution.ExternalSystemTaskExecutionSettings
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable

    public class ExternalSystemTaskExecutionSettings
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Cloneable
    Keeps external system task execution parameters. Basically, this is a model class which holds data represented when a user opens run configuration editor for corresponding external system.
